{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made like a circuit area there, where they only put people like this, you know, like where one member of the family was a war veteran.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father stayed in one room with about, I don't know how many people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother and I and my grandmother, we were in another room but in the same building.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stayed in another room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the floor we had no beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was early-- I mean, for a ghetto, it was really early August '42, because, I think the first Jews from Prague came in '42, in the beginning of '42, maybe late '41.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were actually one of the first German Jews who got there-- not the first, but one of the first German Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was horrendous and very little to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to go to a-- a barrack, where they had the kitchens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you got like a little metal pot, which they called a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And we got the soup and piece of bread and whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was it enough?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't enough, but that's what we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Theresienstadt we were very hungry-- very, very hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother befriended somebody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever heard of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was very well-known from-- Freddy Hersh, have you heard about him?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just want to know if you ever heard about him?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, he was a young man who lived in Prague but originally from Aachen, Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know how my mother met him or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother started working as a, you know, like a helper's nurse or something like to help sick people there.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
